==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undecked
<hw>Un*decked</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
decked; unadorned.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[Eve] <qex>undecked</qex>, save with herself, more lovely fair
Than wood nymph.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not having a deck; <as>as, an <ex>undecked</ex>
vessel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undecolic</ent>⟦br⟧
